BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Chicago
DTSTART:20260404T183000Z
DTEND:20260404T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260404T032118Z
UID:977289
DESCRIPTION:<p>A true New York City institution\, <em>Chicago</em> has eve
 rything that makes Broadway great: a universal tale of fame\, fortune\, an
 d all that jazz\; one show-stopping song after another\; and the most asto
 nishing dancing you&rsquo\;ve ever seen. No wonder <em>Chicago</em> has be
 en honored with six Tony Awards<sup>&reg\;</sup>\, 2 Olivier Awards\, a Gr
 ammy<sup>&reg\;</sup> and thousands of standing ovations.<br /><br />It&rs
 quo\;s also no surprise that <em>Chicago</em> has wowed audiences all arou
 nd the world\, from Mexico City to Moscow\, S&atilde\;o Paulo to South Afr
 ica\, since 1996.<br /><br />Whether you&rsquo\;re looking for your first 
 Broadway musical\, whether you&rsquo\;ve seen the Academy Award&reg\;-winn
 ing film and want to experience the show live onstage\, or whether you&rsq
 uo\;ve seen it before and want to recapture the magic\, <em>Chicago</em> a
 lways delivers.</p>
LOCATION:Ambassador Theatre\, 219 West 49th Street\, New York NY 10019
END:VEVENT
